FBIS3-30583 "dreeu025_p_94006" FBIS-EEU-94-025 Document Type:Daily Report 7 Feb 1994 POLAND KPN Moves for Deputy Prime Minister's Dismissal LD0402144694 Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network in Polish 1200 GMT 4 Feb 94 LD0402144694 Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network Language: Polish Article Type:BFN [Text] The Confederation for an Independent Poland [KPN] has moved for the dismissal of Marek Borowski, deputy prime minister and finance minister. At the same time, the KPN has decided to ask the prosecutor general to investigate the case of privatization of the Bank Slaski [Silesian Bank], in the context of losses suffered by the state budget as the result of the operation.
